body_html:
I had the same problem. It seemed that the converted part failed.
You'd better use bazel_bin command to build the conversion(Not python code). And you should check the tflite file size(1/3 of .data file size). Then when you move the file to you mac os, its small file icon shows the black window which means it is a binary file. That means your conversion is success.
Good luck.
